TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
/*Check for Skeleton records where you have a populated MEDICARE_NUMBER in Salesforce. Use this MEDICARE_NUMBER to check if member is already enrolled in Medicare or MMP. If not enrolled, and record is not already in SF_DSNP_MBR_ALL_MKTS table, then write record to SF_DSNP_MBR_ALL_MKTS table*/ SELECT DISTINCT t.CAID_MEME_CK, t.CAID_SBSB_ID, t.CAID_SBSB_CK, t.PLAN_STATE, t.MEDICAID_NUMBER, t.MEME_HICN, t.PLAN_SITE, sf.SF_ID_ACCT, sf.RECORDTYPEID, sf.CREATEDDATE FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS t INNER JOIN AGP.SFDC_MEMBER sf ON t.MEDICAID_NUMBER = sf.MEDICAID_NUMBER AND sf.RECORDTYPEID = '$$CARE_REC_TYPE' INNER JOIN (SELECT MEME_MEDCD_NO, MAX(m.SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM) AS SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM FROM CMC_MEME_MEMBER m INNER JOIN CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON m.GRGR_CK = g.GRGR_CK AND substr(g.GRGR_ID, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MCR' GROUP BY MEME_MEDCD_NO) u ON t.MEDICAID_NUMBER = u.MEME_MEDCD_NO INNER JOIN CMC_MEME_MEMBER m ON m.MEME_MEDCD_NO = u.MEME_MEDCD_NO AND m.SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM = u.SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM INNER JOIN CMC_MEME_MEMBER m ON sf.MEDICARE_NUMBER = m.MEME_HICN INNER JOIN CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON m.GRGR_CK = g.GRGR_CK AND substr(g.GRGR_ID, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MCR' INNER JOIN CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG e ON m.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK WHERE e.MEPE_EFF_DT = (SELECT MAX(MEPE_EFF_DT) FROM CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG mepe WHERE mepe.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK AND mepe.MEPE_EFF_DT < SYSDATE) AND e.MEPE_ELIG_IND = 'N' AND sf.MEDICARE_NUMBER IS NOT NULL AND sf.MEDICAID_NUMBER IS NOT NULL /*All DSNP Skeleton records in Salesforce should have a MEDICAID_NUMBER*/ AND sf.ACCOUNT_SOURCE = 'DSNP' AND t.MARKET = '$$MARKET' AND t.MEDICAID_NUMBER NOT IN (SELECT m.MEDICAID_NUMBER FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_MBR_ALL_MKTS m WHERE t.MEDICAID_NUMBER = m.MEDICAID_NUMBER AND m.MARKET='$$MARKET')
AND m.MEME_MEDCD_NO NOT IN ( SELECT DISTINCT m.MEME_MEDCD_NO FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS t INNER JOIN CMC_MEME_MEMBER m ON t.MEDICAID_NUMBER = m.MEME_MEDCD_NO INNER JOIN CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON m.GRGR_CK = g.GRGR_CK AND substr(g.grgr_id, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MMP' INNER JOIN CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG e ON m.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK WHERE e.MEPE_EFF_DT = (SELECT MAX(MEPE_EFF_DT) FROM CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG mepe WHERE mepe.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK AND mepe.MEPE_EFF_DT < SYSDATE) AND e.MEPE_ELIG_IND = 'Y' AND t.MARKET = '$$MARKET')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT /*+ PARALLEL(m, 4) */ DISTINCT a.HOME_STREET, a.HOME_CITY, a.HOME_STATE, a.HOME_ZIP, a.COUNTY, a.HOME_COUNTRY, a.EMAIL, a.HOME_PHONE, a.CELL_PHONE, a.OTHER_STREET, a.OTHER_CITY, a.OTHER_STATE, a.OTHER_ZIP, a.OTHER_COUNTRY, e.MEPE_ELIG_IND, e.MEPE_EFF_DT, e.MEPE_TERM_DT, e.SYNERGY_STATUS, e.MBR_PRODUCT, m.CAID_SBSB_ID, m.MCR_HICN, m.MEDICAID_NUMBER, m.FIRST_NAME, m.MIDDLE_INIT, m.LAST_NAME, m.DOB, m.GUARDIAN, m.GENDER, m.LANGUAGE, m.ETHNIC_GROUP, m.AGE, m.PLAN_SITE, p.PRPR_ID, p.PRPR_MCTN_ID, p.PRPR_NAME, p.PRPR_NPI, p.PRAD_ADDRESS, p.PRAD_CITY, p.PRAD_STATE, p.PRAD_ZIP, p.PRAD_PHONE, p.PRAD_FAX, s.PROGRAM_START_DT, s.RENEWAL_DT, s.PROGRAM_END_DT, s.ENROLLED, s.ACTIVE, s.SADI_LOAD_DATE, s.PHONE_NUMBER, m.PLAN_STATE, m.SF_ID_ACCT, m.DSNP_STATUS FROM agp.SF_DSNP_MBR_ALL_MKTS m LEFT JOIN agp.SF_DSNP_ELIG_ALL_MKTS e ON m.CAID_meme_ck = e.CAID_meme_ck AND m.MARKET = e.MARKET LEFT JOIN agp.SF_DSNP_ADDR_ALL_MKTS a ON m.CAID_meme_ck = a.CAID_meme_ck AND m.MARKET = a.MARKET LEFT JOIN agp.SF_DSNP_PCP_ALL_MKTS p ON p.CAID_meme_ck = m.CAID_meme_ck AND p.MARKET = m.MARKET LEFT JOIN agp.SF_DSNP_SAFELINK_ALL_MKTS s ON s.CAID_meme_ck = m.CAID_meme_ck AND s.MARKET = m.MARKET WHERE m.MBR_TYPE = 'MCD' AND m.DSNP_SENT = 1 AND m.MARKET = '$$MARKET'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
/*Check for Skeleton records where you do not have MEDICARE_NUMBER populated in Salesforce. Have to use MEDICAID_NUMBER to get member's Last Name, First Name and Date of Birth from Facets to get MEME_CK to use check if member is already enrolled in Medicare or MMP. If not enrolled, and record is not already in SF_DSNP_MBR_ALL_MKTS table, then write record to SF_DSNP_MBR_ALL_MKTS table*/ SELECT DISTINCT g.GRGR_ID, t.CAID_MEME_CK, t.CAID_SBSB_ID, t.CAID_SBSB_CK, t.PLAN_STATE, t.MEDICAID_NUMBER, t.MEME_HICN, t.PLAN_SITE, sf.SF_ID_ACCT, sf.RECORDTYPEID, sf.CREATEDDATE FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS t INNER JOIN AGP.SFDC_MEMBER sf ON t.MEDICAID_NUMBER = sf.MEDICAID_NUMBER AND sf.RECORDTYPEID = '$$CARE_REC_TYPE' INNER JOIN (SELECT MEME_MEDCD_NO, MAX(m.SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM) AS SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM FROM CMC_MEME_MEMBER m INNER JOIN CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON m.GRGR_CK = g.GRGR_CK AND substr(g.GRGR_ID, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MCR' GROUP BY MEME_MEDCD_NO) u ON sf.MEDICAID_NUMBER = u.MEME_MEDCD_NO
INNER JOIN CMC_MEME_MEMBER m1 ON u.MEME_MEDCD_NO = m1.MEME_MEDCD_NO AND u.SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM = m1.SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM INNER JOIN CMC_MEME_MEMBER m2 ON m1.MEME_LAST_NAME = m2.MEME_LAST_NAME AND m1.MEME_FIRST_NAME = m2.MEME_FIRST_NAME AND m1.MEME_BIRTH_DT = m2.MEME_BIRTH_DT INNER JOIN CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON m2.GRGR_CK = g.GRGR_CK AND substr(g.GRGR_ID, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MCR' INNER JOIN CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG e ON m2.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK WHERE e.MEPE_EFF_DT = (SELECT MAX(MEPE_EFF_DT) FROM CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG mepe WHERE mepe.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK AND mepe.MEPE_EFF_DT < SYSDATE) AND e.MEPE_ELIG_IND = 'N' AND sf.MEDICARE_NUMBER IS NULL AND sf.MEDICAID_NUMBER IS NOT NULL /*All DSNP records in Salesforce should have a MEDICAID_NUMBER*/ AND sf.ACCOUNT_SOURCE = 'DSNP' AND t.MARKET = '$$MARKET' AND t.MEDICAID_NUMBER NOT IN (SELECT m.MEDICAID_NUMBER FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_MBR_ALL_MKTS m WHERE t.MEDICAID_NUMBER = m.MEDICAID_NUMBER AND m.MARKET='$$MARKET') AND m1.MEME_MEDCD_NO NOT IN ( SELECT DISTINCT m.MEME_MEDCD_NO FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS t INNER JOIN CMC_MEME_MEMBER m ON t.MEDICAID_NUMBER = m.MEME_MEDCD_NO INNER JOIN CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON m.GRGR_CK = g.GRGR_CK AND substr(g.grgr_id, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MMP' INNER JOIN CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG e ON m.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK WHERE e.MEPE_EFF_DT = (SELECT MAX(MEPE_EFF_DT) FROM CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG mepe WHERE mepe.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK AND mepe.MEPE_EFF_DT < SYSDATE) AND e.MEPE_ELIG_IND = 'Y' AND t.MARKET = '$$MARKET')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT a.PRAD_ADDR1, a.PRAD_CITY, a.PRAD_STATE, a.PRAD_ZIP, a.PRAD_PHONE, a.PRAD_FAX, p.PRPR_ID, p.PRPR_NAME, p.PRPR_NPI, p.MCTN_ID FROM CMC_PRPR_PROV p left join CMC_PRAD_ADDRESS a on p.prad_id = a.prad_id and a.PRAD_TYPE = 'PRI' and a.PRAD_EFF_DT < SYSDATE and a.PRAD_TERM_DT >= SYSDATE and a.PRAD_ID not like 'TEMP%' and (a.PRAD_ADDR1 is not null OR a.PRAD_ADDR1 <> ' ')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT CAID_MEME_CK, CARE_MEME_CK, PRPR_ID FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT m.CAID_MEME_CK, m.CARE_MEME_CK, mp.PRPR_ID FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_MBR_ALL_MKTS m INNER JOIN CMC_MEPR_PRIM_PROV mp ON m.CAID_MEME_CK = TO_CHAR(mp.MEME_CK ) AND mp.MEPR_PCP_TYPE = 'MP' AND mp.MEPR_EFF_DT < SYSDATE AND MP.MEPR_TERM_DT > SYSDATE WHERE (m.DSNP_STATUS = 'I' AND m.DSNP_SENT = 1) AND m.CARE_MEME_CK is NULL AND m.MARKET = '$$MARKET'
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT m.CAID_MEME_CK, m.CARE_MEME_CK, mp.PRPR_ID FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_MBR_ALL_MKTS m INNER JOIN CMC_MEPR_PRIM_PROV mp ON m.CAID_MEME_CK = TO_CHAR(mp.MEME_CK) AND mp.MEPR_PCP_TYPE = 'MP' AND MP.MEPR_TERM_DT > SYSDATE WHERE (m.DSNP_STATUS = 'I' AND m.DSNP_SENT = 1) AND m.CARE_MEME_CK is NOT NULL AND m.MARKET = '$$MARKET' ) ORDER BY PRPR_ID

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
/*Get Medicaid fields from Facets for Medicare members that are not currently enrolled in Medicare or MMP */ SELECT DISTINCT m.MEME_CK, m.SBSB_CK, m.MEME_HICN, m.SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM, dt.MEDICAID_NUMBER, dt.PLAN_STATE, s.SBSB_ID FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS dt INNER JOIN (SELECT MEME_MEDCD_NO, MAX(m.SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM) AS SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM FROM CMC_MEME_MEMBER m INNER JOIN CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON m.GRGR_CK = g.GRGR_CK AND substr(g.GRGR_ID, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MCR' GROUP BY MEME_MEDCD_NO) u ON dt.MEDICAID_NUMBER = u.MEME_MEDCD_NO
INNER JOIN CMC_MEME_MEMBER m ON m.MEME_MEDCD_NO = u.MEME_MEDCD_NO AND m.SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM = u.SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM
INNER JOIN CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON m.GRGR_CK = g.GRGR_CK AND substr(g.grgr_id, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MCR' INNER JOIN CMC_SBSB_SUBSC s ON m.SBSB_CK = s.SBSB_CK INNER JOIN CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG e ON m.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK WHERE e.MEPE_EFF_DT = (SELECT MAX(MEPE_EFF_DT) FROM CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG mepe WHERE mepe.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK AND mepe.MEPE_EFF_DT < SYSDATE) AND e.MEPE_ELIG_IND = 'N' AND dt.MARKET = '$$MARKET'
AND m.MEME_MEDCD_NO NOT IN ( SELECT DISTINCT m.MEME_MEDCD_NO FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS dt INNER JOIN CMC_MEME_MEMBER m ON dt.MEDICAID_NUMBER = m.MEME_MEDCD_NO INNER JOIN CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON m.GRGR_CK = g.GRGR_CK AND substr(g.grgr_id, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MMP' INNER JOIN CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG e ON m.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK WHERE e.MEPE_EFF_DT = (SELECT MAX(MEPE_EFF_DT) FROM CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG mepe WHERE mepe.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK AND mepe.MEPE_EFF_DT < SYSDATE) AND e.MEPE_ELIG_IND = 'Y' AND dt.MARKET = '$$MARKET')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT DISTINCT m.MEME_LAST_NAME, m.MEME_FIRST_NAME, m.MEME_MID_INIT, m.MEME_SEX, m.MEME_BIRTH_DT, m.SBAD_TYPE_HOME, m.SBAD_TYPE_MAIL, dt.CAID_MEME_CK, dt.CAID_SBSB_ID, dt.CAID_GRGR_ID, dt.CAID_GRGR_CK, dt.CAID_SBSB_CK, dt.PLAN_STATE, dt.MEDICAID_NUMBER, dt.MEME_HICN, dt.PLAN_SITE, to_char(floor (months_between(trunc(sysdate),MEME_BIRTH_DT )/12)) as Age, d.ATUF_TEXT1, t.MCTR_DESC, m.SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS dt INNER JOIN CMC_MEME_MEMBER m ON dt.CAID_MEME_CK = m.MEME_CK INNER JOIN CMC_SBSB_SUBSC s ON m.SBSB_CK = s.SBSB_CK LEFT JOIN CER_ATXR_ATTACH_U a ON s.ATXR_SOURCE_ID = a.ATXR_SOURCE_ID AND a.ATSY_ID = 'RPD' LEFT JOIN CER_ATUF_USERFLD_D d ON a.ATXR_DEST_ID = d.ATXR_DEST_ID AND a.ATSY_ID = d.ATSY_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN CMC_MCTR_CD_TRANS t ON m.MEME_MCTR_LANG = t.MCTR_VALUE AND t.MCTR_TYPE = 'LANG' AND t.MCTR_ENTITY = 'ALL' WHERE dt.MEDICAID_NUMBER NOT IN (SELECT m.MEDICAID_NUMBER FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_MBR_ALL_MKTS m WHERE dt.MEDICAID_NUMBER = m.MEDICAID_NUMBER AND m.MARKET = '$$MARKET') AND dt.MARKET = '$$MARKET'
AND m.MEME_MEDCD_NO NOT IN ( SELECT DISTINCT m.MEME_MEDCD_NO FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS t
INNER JOIN (SELECT MEME_MEDCD_NO, MAX(m.SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM) AS SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM FROM CMC_MEME_MEMBER m INNER JOIN CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON m.GRGR_CK = g.GRGR_CK AND substr(g.GRGR_ID, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MCR' GROUP BY MEME_MEDCD_NO) u ON t.MEDICAID_NUMBER = u.MEME_MEDCD_NO
INNER JOIN CMC_MEME_MEMBER m ON m.MEME_MEDCD_NO = u.MEME_MEDCD_NO AND m.SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM = u.SYS_LAST_UPD_DTM INNER JOIN CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON m.GRGR_CK = g.GRGR_CK AND substr(g.GRGR_ID, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MCR' INNER JOIN CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG e ON m.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK WHERE e.MEPE_EFF_DT = (SELECT MAX(MEPE_EFF_DT) FROM CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG mepe WHERE mepe.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK AND mepe.MEPE_EFF_DT < SYSDATE) AND e.MEPE_ELIG_IND = 'Y' AND t.MARKET = '$$MARKET')
AND m.MEME_MEDCD_NO NOT IN ( SELECT DISTINCT m.MEME_MEDCD_NO FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS t INNER JOIN CMC_MEME_MEMBER m ON t.MEDICAID_NUMBER = m.MEME_MEDCD_NO INNER JOIN CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON m.GRGR_CK = g.GRGR_CK AND substr(g.grgr_id, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MMP' INNER JOIN CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG e ON m.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK WHERE e.MEPE_EFF_DT = (SELECT MAX(MEPE_EFF_DT) FROM CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG mepe WHERE mepe.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK AND mepe.MEPE_EFF_DT < SYSDATE) AND e.MEPE_ELIG_IND = 'Y' AND t.MARKET = '$$MARKET')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT t.MCTR_DESC, TRIM(dt.MEDICAID_NUMBER) FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS dt INNER JOIN CMC_MEME_MEMBER m ON dt.CAID_MEME_CK = m.MEME_CK INNER JOIN CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON m.GRGR_CK = g.GRGR_CK INNER JOIN CMC_SBSB_SUBSC s on m.SBSB_CK = s.SBSB_CK INNER JOIN CMC_MCTR_CD_TRANS t ON s.SBSB_MCTR_VIP = t.MCTR_VALUE and t.MCTR_TYPE = 'VIP' AND t.MCTR_ENTITY = 'SBSB' WHERE (t.MCTR_DESC is not null and t.MCTR_DESC <> ' ') AND dt.MARKET = '$$MARKET'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT d.MEME_CK, d.DUALCTZN_LINK, d.GRGR_CK, e.MEPE_ELIG_IND, m.MEME_HICN, '$$MARKET' AS MARKET FROM CMC_MEME_MEMBER m inner join agp.DUAL_CITIZEN d on m.meme_ck = d.meme_ck and m.grgr_ck = d.grgr_ck inner join CMC_GRGR_GROUP g on m.grgr_ck = g.grgr_ck and substr(GRGR_ID, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MCR' inner join CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG e on d.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK WHERE e.MEPE_CREATE_DTM = (SELECT max(ex.MEPE_CREATE_DTM) FROM CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG ex WHERE ex.meme_ck = e.meme_ck) AND e.MEPE_ELIG_IND = 'N'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Identify MMP records on agp.DUAL_CITIZEN table
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_SF_DUAL_MMP

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT d.MEME_CK, d.DUALCTZN_LINK, d.GRGR_CK, e.MEPE_ELIG_IND, m.MEME_HICN, m.MEME_MEDCD_NO FROM CMC_MEME_MEMBER m inner join agp.DUAL_CITIZEN d on m.meme_ck = d.meme_ck and m.grgr_ck = d.grgr_ck inner join CMC_GRGR_GROUP g on m.grgr_ck = g.grgr_ck and substr(GRGR_ID, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MMP' inner join cmc_mepe_prcs_elig e on d.MEME_CK = e.MEME_CK WHERE e.MEPE_CREATE_DTM = (SELECT max(ex.MEPE_CREATE_DTM) FROM CMC_MEPE_PRCS_ELIG ex WHERE ex.meme_ck = e.meme_ck) AND e.MEPE_ELIG_IND = 'N'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT d.DUALCTZN_LINK, t.CAID_MEME_CK, t.CAID_GRGR_CK, t.MEDICAID_NUMBER FROM agp.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS t inner join agp.DUAL_CITIZEN d on t.CAID_MEME_CK = d.meme_ck and t.CAID_GRGR_CK = d.grgr_ck inner join CMC_GRGR_GROUP g ON t.CAID_GRGR_CK = g.grgr_ck WHERE substr(g.GRGR_ID, 1,5) = '$$MARKET'||'MCD' and t.MARKET = '$$MARKET' and not exists (select 1 from agp.SF_DSNP_CARE_ALL_MKTS c where t.medicaid_number = c.medicaid_number and c.MARKET = '$$MARKET')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
select distinct e.caid_meme_ck, e.caid_grgr_ck, e.cscs_id, A.member_product From AGP.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS e Join ( select cscs_id, regexp_substr ( grgr_ck, '[^,]+', 1, n) as col, member_product from agp.sf_member_product x, (select level n from (select max ( length (grgr_ck) - length (replace (grgr_ck, ','))) as max_commas from agp.sf_member_product) connect by level <= 1 + max_commas) ctr where ctr.n <= 1 + length (grgr_ck) - length (replace (grgr_ck, ',')) ) A ON substr(e.cscs_id, 1,2) = A.CSCS_ID and e.caid_grgr_ck = A.col and length(a.CSCS_ID) = 2 AND e.MARKET = '$$MARKET'
UNION
select distinct e.caid_meme_ck, e.caid_grgr_ck, e.cscs_id, A.member_product From AGP.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS e Join ( select cscs_id, regexp_substr ( grgr_ck, '[^,]+', 1, n) as col, member_product from agp.sf_member_product x, (select level n from (select max ( length (grgr_ck) - length (replace (grgr_ck, ','))) as max_commas from agp.sf_member_product) connect by level <= 1 + max_commas) ctr where ctr.n <= 1 + length (grgr_ck) - length (replace (grgr_ck, ',')) ) A ON substr(e.cscs_id, 1,1) = A.CSCS_ID and e.caid_grgr_ck = A.col and length(a.CSCS_ID) = 1 AND e.MARKET = '$$MARKET'
UNION
select distinct e.caid_meme_ck, e.caid_grgr_ck, e.cscs_id, 'Plus' From AGP.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS e Join (select cscs_id, regexp_substr ( grgr_ck, '[^,]+', 1, n) as col, member_product from agp.sf_member_product x, (select level n from (select max ( length (grgr_ck) - length (replace (grgr_ck, ','))) as max_commas from agp.sf_member_product) connect by level <= 1 + max_commas) ctr where ctr.n <= 1 + length (grgr_ck) - length (replace (grgr_ck, ',')) ) A ON substr(e.cscs_id, 1,2) = A.CSCS_ID and e.caid_grgr_ck != A.col and a.CSCS_ID = 'PL' WHERE e.cscs_id like 'PL%' AND e.MARKET = '$$MARKET'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT t.CAID_MEME_CK, t.MEPE_ELIG_IND, t.MAX_MEPE_EFF_DT, t.MEPE_TERM_DT FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_TMP_ALL_MKTS t INNER JOIN agp.SF_DSNP_MBR_ALL_MKTS m ON t.medicaid_number = m.medicaid_number AND t.MARKET = m.MARKET WHERE m.MBR_TYPE = 'MCD' AND m.DSNP_STATUS = 'I' and m.DSNP_SENT = 1 AND t.MARKET = '$$MARKET'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT m.DSNP_MBR_ID FROM AGP.SF_DSNP_MBR_ALL_MKTS m WHERE not exists (select 1 from AGP.SFDC_DVT_ELIGIBILITY x where m.sf_id_acct = x.account_name__c and extract(year from Eligibility_Expiration_Date__c)||LPAD(extract(month from Eligibility_Expiration_Date__c),2,0) = extract(year from sysdate)||LPAD(extract(month from sysdate),2,0) and Entitled__c in ( 'Pending', 'Y')) AND m.MARKET = '$$MARKET'
